{"article_id":"WQUlhTZ9D5R3FUIf","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"House Republicans revealed their new tax bill Thursday ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"but it 's already encountering some reservations from rank-and-file members .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan described the proposal ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"which lowers the number of tax brackets from seven to four","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"and increases the standard deduction ,","depth":12},{"id":6,"text":"as a series of tax cuts and breaks","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"aimed at helping most Americans .","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"`` It 's very clear and obvious that the whole purpose of this is a middle-class tax cut , ''","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"Ryan said in an interview with CNN 's Phil Mattingly ,","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"shortly after the bill was made public .","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"`` And more to the point , we need to get faster economic growth . ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Ways and Means Committee Chairman Kevin Brady said during Republicans ' news conference","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that the tax bill `` has President","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"( Donald ) Trump 's full support . ''","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"The President issued a statement","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"applauding the bill 's release","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"but added","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"`` there is much work left to do . ''","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"Trump later told reporters in the Oval Office","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that a tax reform bill will be done `` before Christmas , ''","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"calling it `` one of the great Christmas presents . ''","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"However , not all Republicans were happy .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Rep. Lee Zeldin of New York tweeted","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that he planned to vote no on the bill in its current form ,","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"citing the proposal 's elimination of the deduction for state and local taxes ,","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"also known as SALT .","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"`` I am a NO to House # TaxReform bill in its current form .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"A lot of good aspects ,","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"but its not there yet , ''","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"he tweeted ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"linking to a longer statement","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"According to the bill ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"individuals would still be able to deduct their local and state property taxes","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"but only up to $ 10,000 .","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"For that reason , the legislation has struck a nerve with other New York and New Jersey Republicans .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Brady already made a key concession","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"when he said","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"that he said","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"he would still allow individuals to deduct their property taxes in the new bill .","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"But that was n't enough for some","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"who wanted to see the income deduction restored as well .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"The bill ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"called the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act ,","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"would permanently lower the corporate tax rate to 20 %","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"and limit the home interest deduction to loans up to $ 500,000 .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"The bill would also increase the standard deduction for individuals and households ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"repeal the alternative minimum tax","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"and increase the child tax credit to $ 1,600 .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"The House GOP bill would also repeal the estate tax in 2024 .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"According to another source in the GOP meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Brady started his tax presentation with a quote from Ronald Reagan , the last President","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"to sign a massive tax reform bill .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"`` I feel like","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"we just played the World Series of Tax Reform","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"and the American people won , ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Brady said ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"quoting remarks","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Reagan made","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"when signing his tax overhaul from the 1980s .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Brady is a Texas Republican","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"whose Houston Astros won the World Series just hours before .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Despite the optimistic tone","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"set by GOP leaders ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"there are still key questions","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"about what will be in the bill","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and whether the leadership can wrangle the votes","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"they will need","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"to deliver President Donald Trump a major legislative victory by the end of the year .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Now , the hard work begins","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"of both selling the bill","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and keeping special interests at bay .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Many lobbyists on K Street and outside groups admit","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"the GOP lawmakers have kept a tight lid on the process .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Once groups see what has been cut and what has been saved ,","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"winners and losers will be defined","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and the fight","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"to preserve valuable tax breaks","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"will begin .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Over the weekend , one group , the National Association of Home Builders , already came out against the not-even-released bill .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy , a California Republican , notes","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"he 's from a state with high state and local taxes","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"and says","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"pushing for changes","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"need to take a broader look at how the reform package will benefit their constituents .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"`` What 's happening is people are looking at this as one item","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"instead of looking at everything","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"we are doing ,","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"lowering the rate ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"doubling the standard deduction , ''","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"McCarthy told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` You 're better off with this . ''","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"In advance of the bill 's release , some Republicans were already criticizing the details .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"On Thursday , Sen. Marco Rubio tweeted","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that the $ 600 proposed child tax credit increase in the House 's tax reform plan was n't enough .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"`` House # TaxReform plan is only starting point.","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"But $ 600 # ChildTaxCredit increase does n't achieve our & @ POTUS goal","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"of helping working families , ''","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"During a conversation with reporters last Wednesday , Rubio said","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"a $ 2,000 child tax credit was necessary","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to provide tangible relief to middle-class families .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"In 2015 , Rubio ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"joined by Republican Sen. Mike Lee ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"proposed a child tax credit worth $ 2,500 per child .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Republican leaders have argued","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"that the party learned valuable lessons from the health care debate","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that crashed and burned in the Senate this summer .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"But , already , the GOP encountered a setback Tuesday with deadlines","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"when Brady announced","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"that the bill 's release would be delayed by a single day .","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"Some members also fear","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"the GOP 's tax effort in the House has shared some frustrating parallels with Obamacare repeal .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"For one , Republicans are spooked by the ambitious timeline","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"that has been laid out by their leadership .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Members are expecting to get a massive tax bill Thursday","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"only to turn around and amend it in committee days later .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"`` We started differently on tax reform","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"than we did health care ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"but I hope","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"that we do n't end up back on the same tracks","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"that led us to the debacle on health care , ''","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"said Rep. Mark Walker , the chairman of the Republican Study Committee .","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"`` We know","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"this is going to be hundreds of pages","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"and being able to take the time","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"to process it fairly","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"is something that is crucial . ''","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"Another twist","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that came up in the hours","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"before the bill was released","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"came from Trump himself .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"The President tweeted Wednesday morning","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that he wanted to see a repeal of the individual mandate in the tax bill , a move","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"that many House and Senate republicans openly admitted","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"would complicate the process .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"`` Would n't it be great to Repeal the very unfair and unpopular Individual Mandate in ObamaCare","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"and use those savings for further Tax Cuts for the Middle Class .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"The House and Senate should consider ASAP","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"as the process of final approval moves along .","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"Push Biggest Tax Cuts EVER , ''","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"Trump wrote in a series of two consecutive tweets","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"Would n't it be great to Repeal the very unfair and unpopular Individual Mandate in ObamaCare","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"and use those savings for further Tax Cuts .....","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"November 1 , 2017","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"`` I do not believe","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"you are going to see anything health care related in this bill","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"-- at the eleventh hour 59 minute , 58 second mark , I do n't , ''","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"Republican Rep. Chris Collins of New York told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"`` There 's no time","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"to even deal with it ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"that I see , ''","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"Collins said flatly ,","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"`` I believe","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"we are too far along . ''","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"New Jersey GOP Rep. Tom MacArthur ,","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"who has been pressing leaders to maintain a tax deduction for property taxes","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"told reporters","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"he 's still negotiating with leaders ,","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"if he and others from high tax states do n't get what they want in the bill","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"unveiled tomorrow","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"they will keep pushing","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"as the measure moves through the legislative process .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"`` If the bill ca n't pass ,","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"there will be compromises , ''","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"MacArthur said .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"`` I guarantee you that . ''","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"This story has been updated","depth":2},{"id":173,"text":"and will continue to update with additional developments .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":347,"left":345,"right":346,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":345,"left":0,"right":344,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":344,"left":278,"right":343,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":234,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":175,"right":233,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":221,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":193,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":183,"right":192,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":179,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":177,"right":178,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":3,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":181,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":181,"left":8,"right":180,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":